dc_description_s: Extent: 1 atlas (19 unnumbered pages) | Abstract: Atlas of township property maps showing names of rural landowners. | Notes: Earliest publication date estimated by designation of Bristol Road as highway M-121. Latest publication date estimated by designation of a highway M-10 through Flint (rather than the later U.S. 10 Business designation).|Scale determined from section lines. | Scale approximately 1:51,000
